OL,5, A #1bn shortfall in state pension      
OL,6, payments to tens of thousands of women 
OL,7, has been branded "a shameful shambles" 
OL,8, by a committee of MPs.                 
OL,10,FA total of 134,000 pensioners missed   
OL,11,Fout on their full entitlement owing to 
OL,12,Ferrors at the Department for Work and  
OL,13,FPensions (DWP) dating back to 1985.    
OL,15,FSome of those failures risked being    
OL,16,Frepeated during a correction programme,
OL,17,Fthe Public Accounts Committee said.    
OL,19,FThe DWP said it was resolving cases as 
OL,20,Fquickly as possible.                   
